837~170~8,14,On or after the mandated implementation date for the HIPAA National Plan Identifier \040National Plan ID\041\044 XV must be sent\046\r\nPrior to the mandated implementation date and prior to any phasein period identified by Federal regulation\044 PI must be sent\046\r\nIf a phase\045in period is designated\044 PI must be sent unless\058\r\n1\046 Both the sender and receiver agree to use the National Plan ID\044\r\n2\046 The receiver has a National Plan ID\044 and\r\n3\046 The sender has the capability to send the National Plan ID\046\r\nIf all of the above conditions are true\044 XV must be sent\046 In this case the Payer Identification Number that would have been sent using qualifier PI can be sent in the corresponding REF segment using qualifier 2U\046
