837~239~3,1,Line Item Charge Amount
837~239~3,14,This is the total charge amount for this service line\046 The amount is inclusive of the provider\146s base charge and any applicable tax amounts reported within this line\146s AMT segments\046\r\nZero \1470\148 is an acceptable value for this element\046
