837~247,4,Required when there is a paper attachment following this claim\046 \r\nOR \r\nRequired when attachments are sent electronically \040PWK02 \061 EL\041 but are transmitted in another functional group \040for example\044 275\041 rather than by paper\046 PWK06 is then used to identify the attached electronic documentation\046 The number in PWK06 is carried in the TRN of the electronic attachment\046\r\nOR\r\nRequired when the provider deems it necessary to identify additional information that is being held at the provider\146s office and is available upon request by the payer \040or appropriate entity\041\044 but the information is not being submitted with the claim\046 Use the value of \147AA\148 in PWK02 to convey this specific use of the PWK segment\046\r\nIf not required by this implementation guide\044 do not send\046
