837~248,0,The CR1 through CR5 and CRC certification segments appear on both the claim level and the service line level because certifications can be submitted for all services on a claim or for individual services\046 Certification information at the claim level applies to all service lines of the claim\044 unless overridden by certification information at the service line level\046
