837~2~6~CH~1~0,0,Use CH when the transaction contains only fee for service claims or claims with at least one chargeable line item\046 If it is not clear whether a transaction contains claims or capitated encounters\044 or if the transaction contains a mix of claims and capitated encounters\044 use CH\046
