837~320~7~A~1~0,0,Required when the provider accepts assignment\r\nand\047or has a participation agreement with the destination payer\046\r\nOR\r\nRequired when the provider does not accept assignment and\047or have a participation agreement\044 but is advising the payer to adjudicate this specific claim under participating provider benefits as allowed under certain plans\046
