837~512~2,1,Line Item Control Number
837~512~2,14,The maximum number of characters to be supported for this field is \14530\146\046 A submitter may submit fewer characters depending upon their needs\046 However\044 the HIPAA maximum requirement to be supported by any responding system is \14530\146\046 Characters beyond 30 are not required to be stored nor returned by any 837\045receiving system\046
