CAS~0,1,CAS03 is the amount of adjustment\046\r\n\r\nCAS04 is the units of service being adjusted\046\r\n\r\nCAS06 is the amount of the adjustment\046\r\n\r\nCAS07 is the units of service being adjusted\046\r\n\r\nCAS09 is the amount of the adjustment\046\r\n\r\nCAS10 is the units of service being adjusted\046\r\n\r\nCAS12 is the amount of the adjustment\046\r\n\r\nCAS13 is the units of service being adjusted\046\r\n\r\nCAS15 is the amount of the adjustment\046\r\n\r\nCAS16 is the units of service being adjusted\046\r\n\r\nCAS18 is the amount of the adjustment\046\r\n\r\nCAS19 is the units of service being adjusted\046\r\n\r\n
