CR8,0,Pacemaker Certification
CR8,1,To supply information related to Pacemaker registry
CR8~0,1,CR803 is the warranty expiration date\046\r\n\r\nCR804 is the implant date\046\r\n\r\nCR805 is the manufacturer identification\046\r\n\r\nCR806 is the model number\046\r\n\r\nCR807 is the serial number\046\r\n\r\nCR808 indicates if leads were left in the patient\046 A \034Y\034 value indicates leads were left in patient\059 an \034N\034 value indicates leads were not left in patient\046\r\n\r\nCR809 indicates if the pacemaker was returned to the manufacturer\046 A \034Y\034 value indicates the pacemaker was returned to the manufacturer\059 an \034N\034 value indicates the pacemaker was not returned to the manufacturer\046\r\n\r\n
