C003,2,Required for outpatient claims and\047or encounters when an appropriate HCPCS\047HIPPS code exists for this service line item\046\r\nOR\r\nRequired for inpatient claims and\047or encounters when an appropriate HCPCS \040drugs and\047or biologics only\041 or HIPPS code exists for this service line item\046\r\nIf not required by this implementation guide\044 do not send\046
C003,14,This element contains the procedure code that was used to pay this service line\046 It crosswalks from SVC01 in the 835 transmission\046
C003~0,1,C003\04501 qualifies C003\04502 and C003\04508\046\r\nIf C003\04508 is used\044 then C003\04502 represents the beginning value in the range in \r\nwhich the code occurs\046\r\nC003\04503 modifies the value in C003\04502 and C003\04508\046\r\nC003\04504 modifies the value in C003\04502 and C003\04508\046\r\nC003\04505 modifies the value in C003\04502 and C003\04508\046\r\nC003\04506 modifies the value in C003\04502 and C003\04508\046\r\nC003\04507 is the description of the procedure identified in C003\04502\046\r\nC003\04508 represents the ending value in the range in which the code occurs\046\r\n
