C004~0,1,C004\04501 identifies the primary diagnosis code for this service line\046\r\nC004\04502 identifies the second diagnosis code for this service line\046\r\nC004\04503 identifies the third diagnosis code for this service line\046\r\nC004\04504 identifies the fourth diagnosis code for this service line\046\r\n
