329,4,The Transaction Set Control Number in ST02 and SE02 must be identical\046 This unique number also aids in error resolution research\046 Submitters could be sending transactions using the number 0001 in this element and increment from there\046 The number must be unique within a specific interchange \040ISA\045IEA\041\044 but can repeat in other interchanges\046
329,14,The Transaction Set Control Numbers in ST02 and SE02 must be identical\046 The Transaction Set Control Number is assigned by the originator and must be unique within a specific interchange \040ISA\045IEA\041\046 This unique number also aids in error resolution research\046
